	(641,1,'2016-11-23 19:24:09','2016-11-23 19:24:09','[vc_row full_width=\"stretch_row\" content_placement=\"middle\" parallax=\"content-moving\" parallax_image=\"644\" row_alternate_logo=\"1\" css=\".vc_custom_1482179662724{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 250px !important;padding-bottom: 250px !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"Salon offers up-to-date hair services for women and men in a relaxing environment. Our stylists give you personalized attention to make sure you are satisfied every time you visit.\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:left|color:%23ffffff\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css_animation=\"none\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row gap=\"35\" css=\".vc_custom_1479932281934{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 100px !important;padding-bottom: 100px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Welcome to\" font_container=\"tag:h1|font_size:80|text_align:left|color:%23b09d5d|line_height:70px\" google_fonts=\"font_family:Lovers%20Quarrel%3Anormal|font_style:400%20regular%3A400%3Anormal\" css_animation=\"none\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"none\" css=\".vc_custom_1482155884267{margin-top: -30px !important;}\"]\n<h3>    Beauty Salon</h3>\nWe are a full-service salon centrally located in Manhattan.  We have been in business for over 25 years.  Specializing in the art of color, including corrective color and dimensional foil highlighting, we strive to enhance our clients\' inner and outer beauty.\n\nAt Salon Company, we believe in ongoing education!  Because we specialize in color, we have studied with some of the USA\'s leading color experts, including those at the L\'Oreal Professional’s Soho Academy in NYC and in Guilford .  Our Hair Designers go to several workshops and training seminars a year.  We also hold in-house education monthly for our staff.\n\nWe strive to have a fun, uplifting, friendly atmosphere with some of the most professional hair designers around.  When in our salon, you\'ll be treated with great service.  We give thorough and expert consultations before the start of your service. You\'ll know exactly what to expect and what you\'re getting before the start of your service.[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][ozy_vc_regular_carousel navigation_dots=\"false\"][ozy_vc_carousel_item image=\"651\"][ozy_vc_carousel_item image=\"650\"][/ozy_vc_regular_carousel][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row gap=\"35\" css=\".vc_custom_1479933082791{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 100px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_single_image image=\"661\" img_size=\"full\" alignment=\"center\" css_animation=\"none\"][/vc_column][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"none\"]\n<h3>The Story of Salon</h3>\nGina Wild is a family owned brand led by two generations of uniquely skilled hair professionals. Gina has personally played a significant role in the development of <em>modern hairdressing</em> techniques.\n\nWe work with the colouring, hair texture and complexion that nature gives each client and then we optimise and enhance their style, <strong>creating natural looking, beautiful hair</strong>. The salons offer bespoke haircuts, tailored colour services, blowdry services, wedding hair and celebration styling, extensions, ‘permanent’ blowdrys, conditioning treatments and the very best haircare in the business.\n\nJanice wants to thank you in advance for considering her for the opportunity to serve you and your family’s hair care needs.  Added to the best shampoo in the West, she will guarantee you a 5 minute stress relieving scalp massage with relaxing music. All of your cares will go down the drain.  <strong>Guaranteed.</strong>\n\nCutting hair is only part of Janice’s job. Cutting your hair the way you want it is everything. With 25 years experience she is committed to first listening, then cutting. Along with cutting, styling and product knowledge you will have the added value of coloring the hair to compliment your haircut. This in her opinion can take a regular haircut and turn it in to the hair style you\'ve always wanted.\n\nAs a professional she is committed to consistently providing you with excellent customer service. She takes pride in offering you the most current updated looks, and top of the line Paul Mitchell product and color system. She will personally give you the education you deserve on proper product usage. Last, but not least, she is committed to continuing her education, so she can be the best she can be, this she knows is important to you.\n\nAt your scheduled time together, she will look forward to providing you with the best service you will ever experience![/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row parallax=\"content-moving\" parallax_image=\"662\" css_animation=\"fadeIn\" css=\".vc_custom_1479934715350{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 100px !important;padding-top: 150px !important;padding-bottom: 150px !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_custom_heading text=\"A World Class Hair Company\n\" font_container=\"tag:h2|text_align:center|color:%23ffffff\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css_animation=\"none\" css=\".vc_custom_1480073807070{margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 0px !important;}\"][vc_custom_heading text=\"Bespoke colour services, beautiful hairdressing\n\" font_container=\"tag:h4|text_align:center|color:%23ffffff\" use_theme_fonts=\"yes\" css_animation=\"none\" css=\".vc_custom_1480073812289{margin-top: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;}\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row gap=\"35\" css=\".vc_custom_1479935039542{margin-top: 0px !important;margin-bottom: 0px !important;padding-top: 0px !important;padding-bottom: 100px !important;}\"][vc_column width=\"1/2\"][ozy_vc_divider caption_size=\"h4\" caption=\"Client Testimonials\" border_size=\"2\" border_color=\"#000000\" caption_align=\"left\" caption_position=\"top\" more_custom=\"on\