\"fadeIn\"][vc_column_text css_animation=\"fadeIn\" css=\".vc_custom_1480114424874{padding-right: 15% !important;padding-left: 15% !important;}\"]\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #32281b;\">The Salon offer world class colour services and beautiful, bespoke hairdressing. Alex is an award winning colourist that has handpicked and trained his teams to deliver the very best personalised colour, style and experience. Every team member is respectful, inclusive and inspired to deliver a tailored style that supports a unique philosophy – natural beauty enhancement in hair.</span></p>\n[/vc_column_text][vc_btn title=\"MORE\" style=\"custom\" custom_background=\"#56452f\" custom_text=\"#ffffff\" shape=\"square\" align=\"center\" css_animation=\"fadeIn\" row_use_extended_content=\"on\" button_block=\"true\" link=\"url:http%3A%2F%2Fsalon.freevision.me%2Fabout%2F|||\" css=\".vc_custom_1481190007355{padding-right: 27% !important;padding-left: 27% !important;}\"]<img class=\"alignnone wp-image-35 size-large\" src=\"http://twobirdshairandbeautysalon.local/wp-content/uploads/2016/11/shutterstock_83152627-compressor-1024x733.jpg\" alt=\"shutterstock_83152627-compressor\" width=\"1024\" height=\"733\" />\n\nThe Salon is an established hair and beauty centre and specialised skincare clinic in New York, offering a complete hair and beauty makeover and Spa experience.\n\nA professional approach, always up-to-date with the latest developments, and a sincere interest in every person in search of their personal beauty: this is today the key to the success of The Salon, the hair and beauty professionals.\n\nThe aim is for everyone who joins the salon experience to feel inspired, and guided with affection towards realizing themselves.\n\nOpened in 2002 by Alex Wilson, The Salon was born from a strong desire to follow a new kind of approach to the world of hair and beauty and from observing and assessing for the whole of Alex’s professional career the influence that hair